" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Rectal prolapse reduction",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 433px; height: 459px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    (A) The child is placed prone in the knee-chest position on the examination table or the parent's lap. (B) Hold the prolapsed edges with a gauze pad. Using lubricated gloves, apply gentle but firm pressure to reduce the prolapsed mucosa. (C) Digital rectal examination is performed after reduction to ensure that reduction is complete.",
